            </funcprototype>
        </funcsynopsis>
    </refsynopsisdiv>
    <refsect1 xml:id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <function>groupMemoryBarrier</function> waits on the completion of all memory accesses performed
            by an invocation of a compute shader relative to the same access performed by other invocations
            in the same work group and then returns with no other effect.
        </para>
    </refsect1>
